### GET /api/v1/admin/trips
### Descripción: Listar viajes (admin). Requiere rol Admin o Support.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Query: page (default 1), pageSize (default 20)
### Códigos: 200 OK (AdminTripsResponse) | 400 { "error" }

# @name getAdminTrips
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/trips?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "trips": [
#     { "id", "status", "passengerId", "driverId", "pickupAddress", "dropoffAddress", "finalAmount", "createdAtUtc" }
#   ],
#   "totalCount": 0
# }

### Response error (400):
# { "error": "string" }
